11
00:00:50.008 --> 00:00:52.302
<i>But my uncle Toni was a coach</i>

12
00:00:52.385 --> 00:00:54.637
<i>who had a great influence on me.</i>

13
00:00:54.721 --> 00:00:57.682
<i>And helped me with everything.</i>

14
00:00:59.601 --> 00:01:02.604
