when I was very young. you know?

22
00:01:27.337 --> 00:01:29.089
<i>I always trusted him.</i>

23
00:01:29.172 --> 00:01:31.174
[applause]

24
00:01:34.219 --> 00:01:35.929
[Rafa] <i>The match beginsâ€¦</i>

25
00:01:36.888 --> 00:01:41.518
<i>1-0. 2-0. 3-0. 4-0 for the other guy.</i>

26
00:01:41.601 --> 00:01:43.019
[applause]

27
