- [Rafa grunts]
- [ball hitting racket]

84
00:04:59.966 --> 00:05:02.969
- I can push harder. I'm not feeling pain.
- [MaymÃ³] Like yesterday. Easy.

85
00:05:03.052 --> 00:05:05.680
Shit. I have to do
a little more. I need to.

86
00:05:06.264 --> 00:05:07.098
I meanâ€¦

87
