93
00:05:25.658 --> 00:05:27.368
[MoyÃ¡] But you have to be careful. man.

94
00:05:28.286 --> 00:05:29.620
[Rafa] Till it breaks.

95
00:05:32.332 --> 00:05:34.334
[dramatic music playing]

96
00:05:38.504 --> 00:05:40.548
{\an8}[MoyÃ¡] <i>He's very demanding with himself.</i>

97
00:05:41.049 --> 00:05:43.968
{\an8}<i>But if he gets injured again.</i>
<i>then there's nothing.</i>

98
00:05:45.428 --> 00:05:49.682
<i>So. these days.</i>
<i>part of our job is to stop him.</i>

99
00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:54.187
<i> He's been pushed</i>
<i>for so many years to give 100%.</i>

100
00:05:54.687 --> 00:05:56.814
<i>And that made him who he is.</i>

101
00:05:57.482 --> 00:05:59.484
