102
00:06:04.447 --> 00:06:07.325
[Rafa] <i>Since I was a kid.</i>
<i>I enjoyed challenges.</i>

103
00:06:07.408 --> 00:06:08.868
They gave me motivation.

104
00:06:08.951 --> 00:06:11.120
I liked things that were difficult.

105
00:06:13.831 --> 00:06:17.085
<i>But this is because</i>
<i>Toni taught me to be this way.</i>

106
00:06:17.668 --> 00:06:20.254
[Toni] It's not easy. huh? One more time.

107
00:06:20.338 --> 00:06:22.173
I was a demanding coach.

108
00:06:23.758 --> 00:06:25.676
Go! Come on. hit it!

109
00:06:26.552 --> 00:06:29.514
But I was hard on Rafael
because I had great respect for him.

110
00:06:29.597 --> 00:06:31.599
Again. You need to give him hell.

111
00:06:33.184 --> 00:06:35.019
And because he was my nephew.

112
00:06:37.855 --> 00:06:39.440
