177
00:10:40.973 --> 00:10:43.643
[MaymÃ³] <i>And so.</i>
<i>the legend had been created</i>

178
00:10:43.726 --> 00:10:46.771
<i>that Wimbledon was the tournament</i>
<i>you had to win.</i>

179
00:10:47.605 --> 00:10:50.941
<i>Win that and you become</i>
<i>an immortal tennis legend.</i>

180
00:10:51.442 --> 00:10:53.819
