That was the dream. that was the goal.

183
00:11:03.496 --> 00:11:07.208
<i>It had been more than 40 years</i>
<i>since a Spaniard had won there.</i>

184
00:11:08.668 --> 00:11:12.171
[MaymÃ³] <i>It seemed that Spaniards</i>
<i>were not capable of winning on grass.</i>

185
