212
00:12:53.606 --> 00:12:56.108
[commentator 3] <i>Federer</i>
<i>is the best man on the planet.</i>

213
00:12:58.652 --> 00:13:01.489
{\an8}[Roger] <i>I won my first Grand Slam in 2003.</i>

214
00:13:02.072 --> 00:13:03.783
<i>2004. I won three.</i>

215
00:13:04.700 --> 00:13:07.870
And then. 2005. I barely lost matches.

216
00:13:08.454 --> 00:13:11.874
[commentator 1]
<i>Six straight Grand Slam finals.</i>

217
00:13:11.957 --> 00:13:15.044
<i>Every one he has been in.</i>
<i>Roger Federer has won.</i>

218
00:13:15.878 --> 00:13:18.130
[commentator 2] <i>How much more</i>
<i>can this guy achieve?</i>

219
00:13:18.214 --> 00:13:20.633
[interviewer] <i>When you think</i>
<i>you can't get any better. you do.</i>

